            "<p><strong>Emerging Mathematical Ideas</strong></p>",
            "<p>Introduce the term “nested triangles” and broaden understanding of similar triangles.</p>",
            "<p>Use knowledge of similar figures/scale drawings and apply it to nested triangles to solve real world distance problems that are difficult to physically measure.</p>"
